            "id": 5878507,
            "title": "中澤豐(01282):認購基金獨立投資組合",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社28日專訊》中澤豐(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01282:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01282\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01282-HK</a>)公布,於今日,公司全資附屬寶新金融投資,作為認購方,以總代價6000萬元(不包括交易成本)認購基金獨立投資組合,認購總額為6000萬元。(bn)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
